snippet.title: Neo Junk City - Steam Next Fest: February 2025 Demo
snippet.description:
Sinister tides are rising in the Drowned City. Dive into a cyberpunk action-RPG with fast-paced shoot-outs and retro arcade racing. Uncover the truth behind a murder you don't remember committing! Oh, and there is a rat girl in it.

Neo Junk City (C) Josh Hano (The creator of "Nefarious")
Developed by Starblade Games
Release Date: Q4 2025
